      <title>以色列和中东市场因伊朗袭击威胁而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/israeli-stocks-extend-slide-as-fears-of-iran-attack-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们越来越担心伊朗和地区民兵组织准备袭击以色列，这可能标志着地区冲突再次升级，周一中东地区金融市场暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/israeli-stocks-extend-slide-as-fears-of-iran-attack-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 07:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场押注大幅降息，债券市场加速上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球债券市场上涨，因为交易员押注美联储和其他央行将更积极地降息，因为人们越来越担心经济增长放缓的速度比几周前的预期要快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/global-bonds-erase-this-year-s-loss-as-us-economic-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:27:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
